  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defendron is an <strong>epic, action-packed</strong> Tower Defense with a futuristic setting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508740/extras/1881650ce8de3148c366a846704f2a8a.poster.avif?t=1759093325\" width=620 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508740/extras/1881650ce8de3148c366a846704f2a8a.webm?t=1759093325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508740/extras/1881650ce8de3148c366a846704f2a8a.mp4?t=1759093325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5 unique acts</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>25 engaging levels</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Obtain <strong>SDD Upgrade Disks</strong> for semi-permanent upgrade!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 12 </strong>different augments to aid your play!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the challenge with <strong>Malware Disks</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect amazing achievements! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fend off huge waves of enemies! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unveil hidden lore!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508740/extras/bf0a22b51bd6f43daa7f19191232d130.avif?t=1759093325\" width=620 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508740/extras/c446f2e7788bad017f759492d0995466.avif?t=1759093325\" width=620 height=282 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All featuring it's own playstyle, strategy and upgrade path that focuses on it's strengths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508740/extras/e24beb045a5e2b2c0bb709f607926137.avif?t=1759093325\" width=620 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2508740/extras/240a1974b601d40fdf03b6229f885238.avif?t=1759093325\" width=620 height=282 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Modules</strong> are an <strong>alternative path</strong> for upgrading your board!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create countless combinations with a <strong>wide variety of modules</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over <strong>65+ modules available</strong>, that alternates the towers unique features or grants them new <strong>epic abilities</strong>.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Lore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend further into the depths of <strong>Defendron</strong> city, the most secure place in the new world. Get ready to defend yourself against cyberpunk invaders in this <strong>epic tower defense</strong> game set in a futuristic world. With <strong>five acts</strong> set on <strong>different floors</strong> of a towering metropolis, you'll face <strong>increasingly challenging</strong> <strong>waves</strong> <strong>of enemies</strong> as you work your way down from the very top to the bottom of the city. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Defendron</strong>, you must strategically <strong>place and upgrade</strong> a variety of towers to fend off the waves of enemies that move through the city. Each tower has unique abilities and playstyle, which can be altered or enhanced by the modules you mount.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Can you defend the city and emerge victorious in <strong>Defendron</strong>?</h2>",
